summary: Adds an enchanting table, safe, two satchels and a strongbox to the dawnstar sanctuary and sets them not to refresh so you can use it as a player base.
descriptionHtml:
------------------
DESCRIPTION
------------------
Adds 4 new containers and an enchanting table to the Dawnstar Sanctuary.
The Master Bedroom has a strongbox and a safe. The enchanting room a satchel.
and I also added a satchel to the alchemy table.

-------------------
INSTALLATION
-------------------
Extract the .rar file into you \"Skyrim\\Data\" folder and check the box
in your data folder section of the launcher screen. Now you\'re good to go.
author: Amarutu
